phrases: Never before in all the world had such a mysterious phantom manifested...
And whenever that strange figure appeared before people,
they all felt a chill run down their spines...
You are out of places to run, serial jewelry thief!
You really believe you can capture me?!
Was there ever anything more fearsome in this world
than this absolute hollowness, this infinite nothingness?
To the people involved, it was like glimpsing a rip in the fabric of the world.
They shivered in terror, shaken to their very souls...
So this is the kind of story Lucy writes...
I never said you could read it!
So this time it is a story about an invisible person, huh?
W-Well, I thought I would try tackling sort of a different genre, so...
Everybody's thought at least once about what would happen
And I had a feeling I could write an interesting story about it...
You really believe you can capture me?!
What did you two come here for?!
If you have got no reason, then get out!
We are here to invite you out on a job!
If you do not work, you are going to be flat broke.
I am sure you two can handle whatever the job is.
That is not the way it works.
And when we work together as a team, it is got to include you.
Do you have anything to eat around here?
Think I will clear my head with a bath...
I prepared it myself, did not I?
Using this will make my skin so beautiful, it will almost be translucent.
It is been a long time, maybe I will put some on...
I wonder what I could do if that really happened to me.
And maybe it would be useful for work...
I made this ointment seven years ago.
Maybe is got so old that the effect has changed!
I cannot just stay like this!
I need Natsu and the rest to help me!
If I go outside like this, it will because a panic!
No one can see me, so I would better be careful or they will bump into me...
I will stay off to the side.
I came out in a hurry, but now that I think of it, I am naked.
Although come to think of it, now that nobody can see me,
even if I do this weird pose...
Or this pose... or this pose...
Though I feel like an idiot getting excited all by myself...
I would better get to Fairy Tail and fast...
Huh, so Lucy-nee literally booted you out?
Yeah, even though I was there to invite her out on a job!
It is only natural she would be angry.
I hear you two sometimes even use her bath without asking.
That is a flagrant breach of manners.
Even though you are on the same team, a line needs to be drawn.
Whenever you are out of money, come over here and I will feed you.
Although for inconsiderate jerks like you two,
I am sure this goes right over your heads.
But I think she could have been a little nicer to us!
That kind of behavior is the reason she will never be able to snag a boyfriend!
Or even if she got a boyfriend, I bet he would run away first chance he had.
She was born a lady outside, but she is a barbarian on the inside.
Only a Man who was truly wild could be a match for her.
Lucy should learn a little from Team Shadow Gear's Levy!
She should act more like a lady!
I am not all that ladylike myself, but still...
So I am the butt of their jokes when they think I am not here...
What the hell'd you do that for?!
You just doused me with a mug of booze!
Do not go making weird accusations!
If it was not you, then who did it?!
You are the one that started it!
What is going on all of a sudden?
Something about getting splashed with booze...
If you are going to fight, take it elsewhere!
Just when I was getting into it...
What the hell are you doing?!
Do not bug me when I am eatin'!
We are tryin' to have a fight here!
Seven years have passed and you still have not picked a job?!
I am looking for the job that only I can do!
This is no different than usual.
But at this rate, they will destroy the guild hall!
We can always fix it later.
Not getting upset by every little thing is the mark of an adult.
Honestly, this bunch has not matured at all.
If anything, they have become even more boisterous these past seven years...
You have taken it too far!
It looks like Erza has not matured any either.
It is become a regular riot!
The cat's out of the bag!
S-Stop staring at me like that.
For now, we rounded up some clothes for you, but...
You cannot change back to normal?
I came here because I thought you guys could do something...
I do not see what the problem is.
It could be a lot of fun, so let us go out on a job with you like that!
Does not anyone know of a way to cancel out invisibility magic?!
Toasting you with flames will probably fix it!
Y-You have grounds to believe that?
True, when I turned to stone that one time, he did the same thing to me.
But if we cannot think of anything else, I guess that is the only way to go.
If you are a Man, you will do it without hesitation.
I am not mentally prepared yet!
Hmm, looks like it did not work...
I am sure we will find a way...
I believe a time like this is made for me to step up.
Do you have some kind of plan?
All I have to do is paint Lucy's face!
Th-That looks like her and does not look like her at the same time...
Unlike the real Lucy, she is beautiful!
I kind of have mixed feelings...
Then what if I add this?!
I can paint better than that!
Lucy's face is more like this, this, and like this!
No, her eyes are more like this!
Are not her nose and mouth like this?
In that case, there is more of an impact if we go like this.
Let me give it a whack!
I used to take drawing class when I was a kid.
I would go bolder, like so!
It is important to have distinct characteristics.
She is a girl, so we should make her cuter!
Or better yet, how about black hair?
It may look good on her!
I would rather try out a different hairstyle.
Like very short or with dreads...
She would look good with an afro, too, do not you think?
Then we have to paint her face, too!
My face is not a toy!
Why did you make me like this?!
Wow, that looks just like her!
I am sure you have no complaints about this, right?!
A photo from when they did an article on us that time...
For now, make do with that, okay?
Well, this is better than before, but...
We picked up the bottle of ointment and her Celestial Keys.
I can ask my Celestial Spirits for help!
But which Spirit should I summon?
I do not think I could count on Loke or Aquarius at a time like this...
Gate of the Twins, I open thee!
We can keep this up forever!
Still, that is the spitting image of her...
I transform into an exact duplicate.
I can even copy memories and abilities!
In that case, why do not we just say this is the real thing from now on?
After all, the looks and powers are the same...
If anything, this one seems more mild-mannered and easier to get along with...
Fried and Levy, what are you doing?
Analyzing the formulation of the recipe...
If we find out the makeup of the magic,
there may be Runes that can cancel it out.
Fried, these are the ointment's ingredients.
The effects of a magical ointment will be dispelled...
However, the ointment was sitting for seven years...
So it will take seven years to be dispelled.
Not only my body, but now the clothes are becoming invisible?
Your whole existence is starting to disappear!
It is not just Lu-chan becoming invisible,
but she is actually starting to vanish!
On top of that, it will be as if she never existed.
Since it will be as if Lucy never existed, then her things will vanish, too!
I bet her room is empty by now!
I-I do not want this to happen!
I do not want it so I never existed!
I think I was painting something... but what was it?
I feel like someone was standing right here just a second ago...
I feel weird, like something is missing...
Do you feel like that too, Natsu?
Everyone, have you forgotten about me?!
I am not done painting you.
What kind of job would I be able to do?
None of them can hear me...
Then it is just like I am a ghost!
I do not want to be a ghost!
What do you say we go to work?!
Maybe the effect of the ointment was nullified when Natsu remembered her!
Well, like they say, magic takes heart.
And whether it is a little magic or a lot,
nothing can break the bond of the guild!
You talk a good game, but the three of you did not do a thing to help.
When we go to work as a team, it is just got to include you, Lucy!
Sure, it was kind of fun being invisible,
but it was way too lonely when my friends did not notice I was there.
I cannot always count on them, but they are all my dear friends.
I want to get rid of this quick.
I am so glad you are back, Lucy!
Maybe I do wish everyone was a little more level-headed...
He went out on an errand for Mira.
I wish I had a little brother, too...
So I could send him out shopping for me,
and carry my things for me,
and on top of that, I would get the right to have one more fish than him!
Is that how you see those two?
Your mind is too warped, Happy...
